<title>USA: Texas Industries says raising cement prices.</title>
<headline>Texas Industries says raising cement prices.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-08-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Texas Industries Inc said Friday that it will raise prices $5-7 per ton of cement, effective Jan 1, 1998.</p>
